
---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

# Virtual Environment
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Flask / Environment
.env
.flaskenv
instance/app.db

# SQLite
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Node / React
frontend/node_modules/
node_modules/
frontend/dist/
dist/
build/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE / Editor
.vscode/
.idea/

# Cache
.cache/
.pytest_cache/

# Build Files
*.zip
*.exe
*.msi